                            <comment id="12651881" author="fern" created="Sun, 30 Nov 2008 23:04:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;big patch to fix up badly broken DistributedResultSet.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Because it was a big re-write I created a DistributedResultSet2 and DelegatingResultSet2.  Then changed DistributedTemplate and DistributedPreparedStatement to use the new DistributedResultSet2.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It works now, I can now persist objects.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
